---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab's Solution Now Available in SAP App Centre - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab graduates from SAP.iO Foundry Munich's first cohort, making its post-purchase experience solution available in the SAP App Centre."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab's Solution Now Available in SAP App Centre</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2020-01-09">January 9, 2020</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab is delighted to have taken part and graduated from SAP.iO Foundry Munich's first cohort this autumn. The program was created to help accelerate Germany's most promising start-ups. SAP customers can now easily download parcelLab's innovative product from the App Centre and provide seamless post-purchase experiences for their customers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What Are SAP.iO Foundries?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The SAP.iO Foundries are SAP's global network for top-tier start-up programs. They allow start-ups to create innovative software that delivers value for SAP customers. The 10-week in-residence program teaches start-ups how to improve all aspects of their business and enables them to gain exposure to SAP customers -- 437,000 in over 180 countries worldwide.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">SAP.iO Foundry Munich: Fall 2019 Commerce and Marketing Program</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab was thrilled to be selected as one of seven B2B technology start-ups to take part in the first Munich cohort of SAP.iO Foundry. A total of 800 businesses were screened; being selected in the first round was a testament to the solution's potential.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The start-ups were selected based on their ability to:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Enhance customer experiences in commerce and marketing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Apply emerging technologies that unlock enterprise data and drive high outcomes</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Acquire customers and show readiness to scale</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          As part of the accelerator program, parcelLab's solution is now fully integrated and available to download on the SAP App Centre. SAP customers can leverage parcelLab to deliver branded, proactive post-purchase experiences that drive customer loyalty and reduce support costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
